extDesc.message: Webpage automation tool for NYU websites.

mfaHelperNeedSetup.message: Before you can enable MFA Helper, you need to set it up first.

mfaSetupDontSupport.message: The current page is not supported by MFA Helper setup guide. Perhaps you have clicked a different button by mistake, or there are some problems with your browser cache. To solve this, you can try to:

mayExitSetup.message: Or, you can disable MFA Helper setup guide using the Exit Setup button.

enterNetIdPassword.message: Enter your **NetID** and **Password**, then click **Login** button. *Note: this plugin only displays the overlay and has no access to your password.*

completeMfa.message: Complete the **Multi-Factor Authentication (MFA)** *(You might need your phone)*. After that, the guide will proceed automatically, please wait until it finishes.

mfaSetupSucceeded.message: MFA Helper has been setup successfully. You can close the page now.

mfaSetupFailed.message: MFA Helper cannot be setup due to some errors. Please try again later.

confirmCancelTimer.message: Are you sure you want to cancel the timer?

emptyDateTime.message: Date and time cannot be empty.

invalidDateTime.message: Date and time must be later than now.

notInCartPage.message: Please click **Valid / Enroll / Edit** button, and select courses you want to enroll in.

emptyCourse.message: Please select at least one course.

confirmEnrollCourses.message: Are you sure you want to enroll in the following courses:

openCartPage.message: Click **Valid / Enroll / Edit** button, go to the shopping cart page.

selectCourses.message: Select the courses you want to enroll in.

setDateTime.message: Set the enrollment date and time in the popover.

clickStart.message: If everything goes well, the status indicator will become **Waiting**.

onlyNeedToWait.message: The plugin will automatically complete the enrollment procedure. You only need to wait for the results.
